# Rating

Star rating control for feedback input. It supports half-star precision, read-only display, custom colors, custom icons, sizing, and click animation.

## Basic Usage

### Half-star Rating

Use `precision="0.5"` for half-step ratings. Half stars fill from the left side.

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingBasicDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const score = ref(3.5)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating v-model="score" :precision="0.5" show-text />
  </template>
---
::

## Style Customization

Use `filled-color`, `empty-color`, `hover-color`, `text-color`, `size`, and `gap` to tune the visual style. The demo includes orange, green read-only, and compact violet appearances.

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingStyleDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const score = ref(4)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating
      v-model="score"
      :size="28"
      :gap="6"
      :precision="0.5"
      filled-color="#f97316"
      empty-color="rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.34)"
      hover-color="#fb923c"
      text-color="var(--tx-color-warning)"
      show-text
    />
  </template>
---
::

## Custom Icons

Set `icon` to reuse one icon for all states, or use `filled-icon`, `empty-icon`, and `half-icon` separately. Built-in icons, Iconify classes, and emoji are supported, including hearts, diamonds, and face icons.

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingIconDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const mood = ref(3)
  const hearts = ref(4.5)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating v-model="mood" icon="💎" :size="26" filled-color="#38bdf8" show-text />
    <TxRating
      v-model="hearts"
      :precision="0.5"
      :size="28"
      icon="i-carbon-favorite-filled"
      filled-color="#f43f5e"
      empty-color="rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.18)"
      show-text
    />
  </template>
---
::

## Click Animation

Rating plays a more visible bounce + glow + ripple animation after a click by default. Set `:animated="false"` to disable it.

::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="RatingAnimationDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const animated = ref(2)
  const still = ref(2)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxRating v-model="animated" :precision="0.5" show-text />
    <TxRating v-model="still" :animated="false" filled-color="#a78bfa" show-text />
  </template>
---
::

## Interaction Contract

Rating exposes the star group as a radio group. `disabled` and `readonly` both block updates; `readonly` is display-only and removes star button interaction while keeping the rating visible.

## API (Lite)
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: modelValue
    type: number
    default: '0'
    description: Current score
  - name: maxStars
    type: number
    default: '5'
    description: Total stars
  - name: precision
    type: "number | 0.5"
    default: '1'
    description: Step size
  - name: showText
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: Show score text
  - name: disabled
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: Disable interaction
  - name: readonly
    type: boolean
    default: 'false'
    description: Display-only mode
  - name: icon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: '-'
    description: Shared rating icon
  - name: filledIcon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: 'star'
    description: Filled icon
  - name: emptyIcon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: 'star'
    description: Empty icon
  - name: halfIcon
    type: "string | TxIconSource"
    default: '-'
    description: Half icon; when omitted, Rating clips the filled layer from the left
  - name: filledColor
    type: string
    default: '#fbbf24'
    description: Filled color
  - name: emptyColor
    type: string
    default: '#d1d5db'
    description: Empty color
  - name: hoverColor
    type: string
    default: 'filledColor'
    description: Hover color
  - name: textColor
    type: string
    default: '#6b7280'
    description: Score text color
  - name: size
    type: "number | string"
    default: '20px'
    description: Star icon size
  - name: gap
    type: "number | string"
    default: '2px'
    description: Gap between stars
  - name: animated
    type: boolean
    default: 'true'
    description: Play the click pop animation
---
:::

